Package main.net.atos.uk.TravelDashboard.Dashboard.Report

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DateSelector
    This class is used to find all date options of several ComboBoxs in: main Dashboard and report page.
    PDFGenerator
    This class is used to generate the PDF document of the report, to the OS Desktop.
    Recorder
    This class defines a type to have a place name and the total amount.
    ReportCentreController
    This class is the controller class of the report page.
    ReportDataCalculator
    This class is used to generate analysis data and charts for the report page: the labels and charts of five part: general information, time, location, cost element and member.
